Subject: drm/i915/gt: Mark up intel_rps.active for racy reads
Git-commit: 74e5a9aca01e77ea3f5e4b7b1d010249d600ca0e
Patch-mainline: v5.7-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

We read the current state of intel_rps.active outside of the lock, so
mark up the racy access.

